FAQ:
Q: Can I use this in my video? 
A: Go for it! Just be sure to give proper credit :)

Q: 1 hour version? 
A: Nah, you've got the loop function for that :P

====

Original song by Lena Raine as part of Minecraft's Nether Update - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BTthtlT80Rc
Cover art by Noël Risco - https://twitter.com/noel_risco/
Music made with Logic Pro X
Visuals made in Adobe After Effects CC
